{"id":"7243","name":"bright-early-sweating-bullets-edition","title":"Bright &amp; Early: Sweating Bullets Edition","author":"Christy Frink","date":"2011-06-01T10:00:00-05:00","tags":[],"categories":["News"],"contentEncoded":"<div id=\"greet_block\"><noscript><div class=\"greet_block wpgb_cornered\"><div class=\"greet_text\"><div class=\"greet_image\"><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/feed/rss/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"http://nashvillest.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-greet-box/images/rss_icon.png\" alt=\"WP Greet Box icon\"></a></div>Hello there! If you&apos;re new to Nashvillest, you might want to <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/nashvillest\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>subscribe to our RSS feed</strong></a> to make sure you don&apos;t miss anything! We&apos;re also on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/nashvillest\" target=\"blank\"><strong>Twitter</strong></a> if you&apos;d like to join us there!<div style=\"clear:both\"></div><div class=\"greet_block_powered_by\">Powered by <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/projects/wordpress-plugins/wp-greet-box-wordpress-plugin/\" title=\"WP Greet Box WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WP Greet Box</a> <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/\" title=\"WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WordPress Plugin</a></div><div style=\"clear:both\"></div></div></div></noscript></div><p><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/callrw/5777757179/in/pool-715021@N24/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.flickr.com&apos;]);\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2420/5777757179_6cb261fe5e.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"322\"></a></p><p>Good morning, Nashville. We&#x2019;re tight on time this morning, so you know the drill:</p><ul><li>Talk about a heat wave! Temperature records &#xA0;are being tied and broken all week. Remember that time it took us all 4 hours to get home from work because it was snowing? [<a href=\"http://nashvillewx.com/2011/05/close-to-records-this-week/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;nashvillewx.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Nashville WX</a>]</li><li>Good thing the pools are opening this week. [<a href=\"http://www.wkrn.com/story/14766262/pools-open-as-temperatures-near-record-high\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wkrn.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WKRN</a>]</li><li>Wave Country, on the other hand, is still trying to figure out how to prevent riots like the one they saw this weekend. [<a href=\"http://www.tennessean.com/article/20110601/NEWS/306010073/2275/RSS05\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.tennessean.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Tennessean</a>]</li><li>No, Vanderbilt is not paying $300 or $3,000 or $10,000 for blue-eyed cicadas. [<a href=\"http://www.tennessean.com/article/20110601/NEWS/306010090/2275/RSS05\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.tennessean.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Tennessean</a>]</li><li>That empty old 12-story high rise at 4th and Union may soon turn into a fancy hotel. [<a href=\"http://www.wsmv.com/news/28092189/detail.html\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wsmv.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WSMV</a>]</li><li>Hang in there, Bellevue! You&#x2019;re a few steps closer to having your first wine and liquor store. [<a href=\"http://www.wkrn.com/story/14753387/plans-for-first-ever-bellevue-liquor-store-move-forward\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wkrn.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WKRN</a>]</li><li>The famous 400-mile yard sale that runs clear across our neighboring state of Kentucky starts tomorrow and runs through Sunday. [<a href=\"http://www.newschannel5.com/story/14758433/400-mile-sale-held-across-kentucky-this-week\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.newschannel5.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WTVF</a>]</li><li>Police are already warning us about Bonnaroo traffic. [<a href=\"http://www.wsmv.com/news/28086001/detail.html\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wsmv.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WSMV</a>]</li></ul><p><em>Photo by <a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/callrw/5777757179/in/pool-715021@N24/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.flickr.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Richard Call</a></em>.</p><p>No related posts.</p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<!--END .entry-content .article-->"}